Package: conary
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Modern package manager with atomic operations and delta updates
 Conary brings atomic transactions, automatic rollback, and delta updates
 to Linux systems. Works alongside existing package managers (DNF, APT, pacman).
